# PROXY / SQUID / PROTECTION INTERNET

## Squid sur pfSense

### Installation

```text
System > Package Manager > Available Packages

Installer : Squid
```

---

# CONFIGURATION SQUID

```text
Services > Squid Proxy Server
```

## Général

```text
Enable Squid Proxy
Enable Access Log
Transparent HTTP Proxy
Enable SSL Filtering
```

## Cache

```text
Hard Disk Cache Size : 1024 MB
```

## Logs

```text
Rotate Logs : 365
```

## Blacklist

```text
ACL > Blacklist

www.yahoo.fr
facebook.com
youtube.com
```

---

# TESTS

## Vérifier accès Internet

```text
Diagnostics > Ping

